{"title_page": "Iskandar Dzhalilov", "text_new": "{{short description|Tajikistani footballer|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| image       = \n| name        = Iskandar Dzhalilov\n| fullname    = Iskandar Fatkhulloyevich Dzhalilov\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1992|6|1|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = [[Dushanbe]], [[Tajikistan]]\n| height      = {{height|m=1.80}}\n| position    = [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|Right back]]\n| currentclub = [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]]\n| clubnumber  = 5\n| youthyears1 = 2008\u20132010 | youthclubs1 = [[PFC CSKA Moscow|CSKA Moscow]]\n| years1  = 2010\u20132014 | clubs1  = [[FC Rubin Kazan|Rubin Kazan]]                                  | caps1  =  0 | goals1  = 0\n| years2  = 2012      | clubs2  = \u2192 [[FC Neftekhimik Nizhnekamsk|Neftekhimik]] (loan)             | caps2  =  0 | goals2  = 0\n| years3  = 2013      | clubs3  = \u2192 [[CS Turnu Severin|Turnu Severin]] (loan)                     | caps3  = 11 | goals3  = 0\n| years4  = 2013      | clubs4  = \u2192 [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]] (loan)                               | caps4  =  5 | goals4  = 0\n| years5  = 2014\u20132016 | clubs5  = [[FC Volga Nizhny Novgorod|Volga Nizhny Novgorod]]              | caps5  = 35 | goals5  = 0\n| years6  = 2016\u20132017 | clubs6  = [[FC Dunav Ruse|Dunav Ruse]]                                    | caps6  = 26 | goals6  = 0\n| years7  = 2017\u20132018 | clubs7  = [[FC Baltika Kaliningrad|Baltika Kaliningrad]]                  | caps7  = 17 | goals7  = 0\n| years8  = 2018      | clubs8  = [[PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv|Lokomotiv Plovdiv]]                     | caps8  =  2 | goals8  = 0\n| years9  = 2018      | clubs9  = [[POFC Botev Vratsa|Botev Vratsa]]                              | caps9  =  0 | goals9  = 0\n| years10 = 2019\u2013     | clubs10 = [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]]                                        | caps10 = 18 | goals10 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = 2009  | nationalteam1 = [[Russia national under-17 football team|Russia U-17]] | nationalcaps1 = 18 | nationalgoals1 = 2\n| nationalyears2 = 2010  | nationalteam2 = [[Russia national under-18 football team|Russia U-18]] | nationalcaps2 =  6 | nationalgoals2 = 0\n| nationalyears3 = 2011  | nationalteam3 = [[Russia national under-19 football team|Russia U-19]] | nationalcaps3 =  4 | nationalgoals3 = 0\n| nationalyears4 = 2014\u2013 | nationalteam4 = [[Tajikistan national football team|Tajikistan]]       | nationalcaps4 = 20 | nationalgoals4 = 0\n| pcupdate = 16:09, 12 April 2020 (UTC)\n| ntupdate = 14 November 2019\n}}\n'''Iskandar Dzhalilov''' ({{lang-tg|\u0418\u0441\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440 \u04b6\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043b\u043e\u0432}}; born 1 June 1992) is a [[Tajikistan]]i [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[FC Istiklol]]. Dzhalilov holds [[Russia]]n citizenship, and is second cousins of fellow footballers [[Manuchekhr Dzhalilov]] and [[Alisher Dzhalilov]].\n\n==Career==\nIn September 2013, Dzhalilov moved on loan from [[FC Rubin Kazan]] to [[FC Istiklol]],<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ru:\u0418\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u043b\u043e\u043b \u0430\u0440\u0435\u043d\u0434\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043b \u0418\u0441\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0430 \u0414\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043b\u043e\u0432\u0430 \u0434\u043e \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0446\u0430 \u0441\u0435\u0437\u043e\u043d\u0430|url=http://fc-istiklol.tj/index.php?view=1&news=51|website=fc-istiklol.tj|publisher=[[FC Istiklol]]|accessdate=13 October 2014|language=Russian|date=4 September 2013}}</ref> returning to Rubin in January 2014 after his loan deal with  expired.<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ru:\u0417\u0430\u043a\u043e\u043d\u0447\u0438\u043b\u0441\u044f \u0441\u0440\u043e\u043a \u0430\u0440\u0435\u043d\u0434\u044b \u0418\u0441\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0430 \u0414\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043b\u043e\u0432\u0430|url=http://fc-istiklol.tj/index.php?view=1&news=203|publisher=[[FC Istiklol]]|accessdate=10 October 2014|language=Russian|date=16 January 2014}}</ref>\n\nHe made his [[Russian National Football League]] debut for [[FC Volga Nizhny Novgorod]] on 6 July 2014 in a game against [[FC Sibir Novosibirsk]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Russian National Football League]]|url=http://www.1fnl.ru/players/1254/|title=Career Summary|date=5 September 2014}}</ref> Dzhalilov relocated to [[Bulgaria]] in July 2016, signing a contract with newly promoted [[First Professional Football League (Bulgaria)|Bulgarian First League]] football club [[FC Dunav Ruse|Dunav Ruse]].<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.glas.bg/228927/dunav-podpisa-s-yunosha-na-cska-moskva.html|title=\u0414\u0443\u043d\u0430\u0432\" \u043f\u043e\u0434\u043f\u0438\u0441\u0430 \u0441 \u044e\u043d\u043e\u0448\u0430 \u043d\u0430 \u0426\u0421\u041a\u0410 (\u041c\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0432\u0430) |date=7 July 2016|accessdate=9 July 2016 |language=Bulgarian |publisher=glas.bg}}</ref> He was released in June 2017.<ref>{{cite web | title = \u0424\u041a \"\u0414\u0443\u043d\u0430\u0432\" \u0441\u0435 \u0440\u0430\u0437\u0434\u0435\u043b\u0438 \u0441 \u0442\u0440\u0438\u043c\u0430, \u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u0438 \u0441\u0435\u0440\u0438\u043e\u0437\u043d\u043e \u043f\u043e \u0441\u0435\u043b\u0435\u043a\u0446\u0438\u044f\u0442\u0430 | url = http://fcdunav.eu/5889-2/ | publisher = fcdunav.eu | date = 6 June 2017 | language = Bulgarian}}</ref>\n\nOn 5 July 2017, Dzhalilov signed with [[Russia]]n side [[FC Baltika Kaliningrad|Baltika Kaliningrad]] for 1+1 years.<ref>{{cite web | title = \u041e\u0434\u0438\u043d\u043d\u0430\u0434\u0446\u0430\u0442\u044b\u0439 \u043d\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0435\u0446 | url = http://www.fc-baltika.ru/news/odinnadcatyj-novobranec | publisher = fc-baltika.ru | date = 5 July 2017 | language = Russian}}</ref>\n\nOn 19 June 2018, Dzhalilov returned to [[Bulgaria]], signing for two years with [[PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv|Lokomotiv Plovdiv]].<ref>{{cite web | title = \u041b\u043e\u043a\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0442\u0438\u0432 \u043f\u043e\u0434\u043f\u0438\u0441\u0430 \u0434\u043e\u0433\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0440 \u0441 \u0418\u0441\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440 \u0414\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043b\u043e\u0432 | url = https://lokomotivpd.com/lokomotiv-podpisa-dogovor-s-iskandar-dzhalilov/ | publisher = lokomotivpd.com | date = 19 June 2018 | language = Bulgarian}}</ref> On 30 July 2018 Dzhalilov's contract with Lokomotiv Plovdiv was cancelled by mutual consent.<ref>{{cite web |title=\u041b\u043e\u043a\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0442\u0438\u0432 \u0441\u0435 \u0440\u0430\u0437\u0434\u0435\u043b\u0438 \u0441 \u0418\u0441\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440 \u0414\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043b\u043e\u0432 \u0438 \u0410\u043d\u0442\u043e\u043d\u0438 \u041c\u0438\u043b\u0438\u043d\u0430 |url=https://lokomotivpd.com/lokomotiv-se-razdeli-s-iskandar-dzhalilov-i-antoni-milina/ |website=lokomotivpd.com/ |publisher=PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv |accessdate=1 August 2018 |language=Bulgarian |date=30 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n===Club===\n{{updated|match played 12 April 2020}}<ref name=\"NFT Stats\"/><ref>{{cite web|title=I.Dzhalilov|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/iskandar-dzhalilov/250507/|website=soccerway.com/|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=30 January 2015}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" valign=\"center\"|[[FC Rubin Kazan|Rubin Kazan]]\n|[[2010 Russian Premier League|2010]]\n|rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"center\"|[[Russian Premier League]]\n|0||0||0||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||0||0\n|-\n|[[2011\u201312 Russian Premier League|2011\u201312]]\n|0||0||0||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||0||0\n|-\n|[[2012\u201313 Russian Premier League|2012\u201313]]\n|0||0||0||0||0||